    "body": "@francoischalifour @Haroenv \r\n\r\n1. Do we just want to throw an error at rollup when VERSION is not given?\r\n\r\n2. Or, do we still need UNRELEASED for some reason? If so, what is a valid case for that?\r\n\r\nIf you're not sure about (2), we could go for (1) first and see if we get any errors. wdyt?",
